2.02
Hover & click on the images for description

Description

Description:
Skips the current loop iteration, continues with the next one and returns the given value.
Groups:
Program Flow
Syntax

Syntax:
continueWith returnParameters:
return: Anything - value to be returned when iteration is skippedReturn Value:
Anything
Examples

Example 1:Copy// results in [2, "TEST", 4]
private _result = [1, 2, 3] apply {
if (_x == 2) then {
continueWith "TEST";
	} else {
_x + 1;
	};
};

Additional Information

See also:
