Syntax:
map ctrlMapSetPosition [x, y, w, h]Parameters:
map: Control - Map control
x: Number - (Optional) Left top x of map control
y: Number - (Optional) Left top y of map control
w: Number - (Optional) Width of map control
h: Number - (Optional) Height of map controlReturn Value:
Nothing
Examples

Example 1:Copy_map ctrlMapSetPosition [0,0,1,1];Example 2:Copy_map ctrlSetPosition [0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5];
